divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband and I took pictures of the sunset at The Aerie, west of Doe Mountain in Sedona, Arizona. While we were waiting for the sun to set, I took pictures of the surrounding area. Neither my husband nor I witnessed any object in the sky while I was taking the attached shot. Tonight I transferred the photos from my camera to my computer and I found a shot with an object that I cannot identify. I am hoping a photo expert can rule out a cloud or a flying bug.
